程序包 org.jacoco.examples

  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    ClassInfo
    This example reads Java class files, directories or JARs given as program arguments and dumps information about the classes.
    CoreTutorial
    Example usage of the JaCoCo core API.
    CoreTutorial.MemoryClassLoader
    A class loader that loads classes from in-memory data.
    CoreTutorial.TestTarget
    The test target we want to see code coverage for.
    ExecDump
    This example reads execution data files given as program arguments and dumps their content.
    ExecutionDataClient
    This example connects to a coverage agent that run in output mode tcpserver and requests execution data.
    ExecutionDataServer
    This example starts a socket server to collect coverage from agents that run in output mode tcpclient.
    MBeanClient
    This example connects to a JaCoCo agent that runs with the option jmx=yes and requests execution data.
    ReportGenerator
    This example creates a HTML report for eclipse like projects based on a single execution data store called jacoco.exec.
